&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in managing the month end and quarter accounting close activities for clinical related R&amp;amp;D accruals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the preparation and maintenance of monthly clinical tracker, ensuring expenses, prepayments and deposits, and accrual accountsare accurately captured timely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare journal entries, account reconciliations and related supporting workpapers in accordance with US GAAP and comply with our internal SOX requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review the CRO budget tracker and incorporate appropriate estimates provided by CRO into in the clinical tracker and ensure alignment with contractual obligations and study progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
